Full-Time
Travel Industry Revenue Manager – Must have UAE experience
–
Dubai, Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Job Description
The successful candidate will be responsible for:
Managing of revenues from sales of tickets to corporate and retail customers
Managing payment to the airlines and address any discrepancies including incorrect fare collected on the ticket, and tax
Completing the processing and accounting of customer invoices, sales, discounts, and other related accounts
Managing 3 retail operations
Experience & Skills
Minimum 3 years’ accounting and revenue management in an airlines, tour operators or travel agency
Advanced knowledge of airlines accounting and revenue management
Team leadership and management
Qualifications
Minimum M.Com
